<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.5">
<l>karaicey mākkaṭaṟ kiṭantavaṉ kaṉaikaḻa</l>
<l>lamararkaḷ toḻutētta</l>
<l>araicey mēkalai yalarmaka ḷavaḷoṭu</l>
<l>mamarntanal limayattu</l>
<l>varaicey mākkaḷi ṟiḷavetir vaḷarmuḷai</l>
<l>yaḷaimiku tēṉṟōyttu</l>
<l>piraca vāritaṉ ṉiḷampiṭik karuḷceyyum</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where rests the sleeper on the vast, roaring sea,</l>
<l>With the lady of the lotus, a girdle shaping her waist,</l>
<l rend="indent">as immortals praise [him], worshipping his rattling anklets,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where a huge elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">made like a mountain, dipping tender grown bamboo shoots</l>
<l>Into the honey which filled a [tree] hollow, gathering honey,</l>
<l rend="indent">graciously gives [it] to his young mate.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
